name: Dafne de Dios Couture
description:
Created by Puerto Rican artist Dafne de Dios, these two pieces of fine gold and aqua colored lace are one of her limited and exclusive creations inspired in the women who enjoy their sexuality. Strips in the top allows you to adjust for more or less opening in the bust.  The skirt has precious lined buttons of the same fabric in the back and falls on the hip which makes this attire more exotic but in an elegant fashion. 

This exclusive dress fits a bust of 32" to 35" and hip of 35" to 38". 

If interested, email to ask for pictures of the details of the piece such as sewing quality, fabric color and texture and artist name label.  

.This two piece dress is a fine work of art and is not-refundable.

.Other exclusive creations available for show. 

Contact info: dafnewm@yahoo.com
